Performance

“Each year one of our goals is to provide sector leading NOI growth and Core FFO growth per share. Over time this has led to significant long-term dividend growth and share price growth, providing a total 10-year return that is not only the highest of all public REITs, but among the highest of any public company of our size in the United States.”
